FuncDef:
The display default-parameter ospf command displays the default OSPF configuration.
The display default-parameter ospfv3 command displays the default OSPFv3 configuration. The display default-parameter ospf command displays the default OSPF configuration. The display default-parameter ospfv3 command displays the default OSPFv3 configuration.

ParaDef.Info:
Display default OSPFv3 configurations.

 NOTE: This parameter is supported only on the CE6863H, CE6863H-K, CE6860-SAN, CE6866K, CE6866, CE6860-HAM, CE6855-48XS8CQ, CE6885-SAN, CE8850-SAN, CE8855, CE8851-32CQ4BQ, CE8851K, CE8851-32CQ8DQ-P, CE8850-HAM, CE6881H, CE6881H-K, CE6820H, CE6820H-K, CE6820S, CE6885, CE6885-T, CE6885-LL (standard forwarding mode) and CE6863E-48S8CQ.
